data.comment: The match has started.
Can Mjallby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in AIK's half?
In the minute 3, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
AIK advance rapidly upfield but Mohammed Al-Hakim blows for offside.
In Hallevik a free kick has been awarded the away team.
In the minute 4, In Hallevik, AIK push forward quickly but are pulled up for offside.
At Strandvallen, AIK are penalized for being offside.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the away team a throw-in.
In the minute 7, Throw-in for AIK at Strandvallen.
Mjallby's Moses Ogbu is on target but unsuccessful.
Corner awarded to Mjallby.
In the minute 9, In Hallevik Mjallby attack through Jonathan Tamimi. The finish is off target, however.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards AIK a goal kick.
Moses Ogbu scores to make it 1-0 at Strandvallen.
In the minute 10, Mohanad Jeahze with an assist there.
Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Mjallby push upfield but Mohammed Al-Hakim quickly pulls them for offside.
In the minute 13, Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Mjallby have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a AIK throw-in in Mjallby's half.
In the minute 19, It's a goal kick for the home team in Hallevik.
Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of AIK.
Free kick for AIK in their own half.
In the minute 23, Throw-in Mjallby.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
AIK have a dangerous throw-in.
In the minute 27, Henok Goitom (AIK) gets up for a header but cannot keep the ball on target.
Mjallby have a goal kick.
Mjallby's Mohanad Jeahze breaks free at Strandvallen. But the strike goes wide of the post.
In the minute 29, Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
Goal kick for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 32, AIK to take a throw-in in Mjallby territory.
Free kick for AIK in the half of Mjallby.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Mjallby just outside AIK's area.
In the minute 35, Robin Tihi (AIK) has been booked and must now be careful not to get a second yellow card.
Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
Throw-in for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
In the minute 38, AIK awarded a free kick in their own half.
AIK have been given a penalty at Strandvallen...
Enock Kofi Adu equalizes with a well-taken penalty.
In the minute 41, A throw-in for the away team on the opposite half.
AIK's Per Karlsson has been booked in Hallevik.
An attacking Mjallby player has been brought down in the area - penalty!
In the minute 43, Goal! Moses Ogbu gives Mjallby the lead from the penalty spot. The score is now 2-1.
Ball safe as AIK is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a AIK throw-in in Mjallby's half.
In the minute 45, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK.
2 minutes of injury time will be added to the 1st half.
In the minute 45, AIK's Henok Goitom gets his shot away but it misses the target.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Hallevik.
Throw-in high up the field for Mjallby in Hallevik.
In the minute 45, AIK's Rasmus Lindkvist is back in action after a slight knock.
It's getting dangerous! Free kick for Mjallby close to the penalty box.
The whistle has gone to end the first-half.
Attention is being given to AIK’s Rasmus Lindkvist and play has been suspended briefly.
In the minute 46, The second-half is underway in Hallevik.
Great shot from Mjallby's Viktor Gustafson but he is denied by the crossbar.
Jesper Lofgren for Mjallby gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.
In the minute 47, Goal kick for AIK at Strandvallen.
Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Corner awarded to AIK.
In the minute 50, AIK have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards AIK a goal kick.
AIK have a goal kick.
In the minute 56, Mjallby push forward at Strandvallen and Moses Ogbu gets in a great header. The attempt is cleared by the AIK defence.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK in their own half.
Throw-in Mjallby.
In the minute 58, Free kick AIK.
Mohanad Jeahze (Mjallby) gets a yellow card.
Free kick AIK.
In the minute 61, Can AIK capitalize from this throw-in deep inside Mjallby's half?
AIK surge into the attack at Strandvallen but Stefan Silva’s header is off-target.
Goal kick for Mjallby at Strandvallen.
In the minute 62, In Hallevik a free kick has been awarded the away team.
Bartosz Grzelak is making the team's third substitution at Strandvallen with Nabil Bahoui replacing Stefan Silva.
Ebenezer Ofori is replacing Enock Kofi Adu for AIK at Strandvallen.
In the minute 62, Bartosz Grzelak (AIK) is making a first substitution, with Eric Kahl replacing Rasmus Lindkvist.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
AIK to take a throw-in in Mjallby territory.
In the minute 64, AIK needs to be cautious. Mjallby have an attacking throw-in.
Ball goes out of play for a AIK goal kick.
AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
Mjallby drives forward and Mamudo Moro gets in a shot. Without netting, however.
In the minute 66, AIK make their fourth substitution with Robert Lundstrom replacing Robin Tihi.
Nabil Bahoui (AIK) goes for goal but the shot is blocked by an alert defence.
In the minute 68, Corner awarded to AIK.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards the home team a throw-in.
Can AIK get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Mjallby's half?
In the minute 71, Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
AIK awarded a throw-in in their own half.
The home team have replaced Mamudo Moro with Taylor Silverholt. This is the first substitution made today by Marcus Lantz.
In the minute 74, Free kick for Mjallby in the half of AIK.
David Lofquist (Mjallby) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a throw-in for Mjallby, close to AIK's area.
In the minute 76, Taylor Silverholt heads in to give Mjallby a 3-1 lead at Strandvallen.
Max Watson instrumental with a fine assist.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK.
In the minute 79, Ball safe as Mjallby is awarded a throw-in in their half.
Tom Strannegard is replacing Felix Michel Melki for AIK at Strandvallen.
Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 82, Ebenezer Ofori (AIK) gets in a strike but the shot is blocked by a defender.
AIK are pushing forward but Karol Mets's finish is wide of the goal.
It's a goal kick for the home team in Hallevik.
In the minute 82, The home team replace Viktor Gustafson with David Batanero.
Throw-in for AIK close to the penalty box.
AIK drive upfield and Nabil Bahoui gets in a shot. The strike is blocked by a Mjallby defender.
In the minute 84, Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to Mjallby in their own half.
Throw-in AIK.
The home team have replaced David Lofquist with Adam Petersson. This is the third substitution made today by Marcus Lantz.
In the minute 87, AIK have been awarded a corner by Mohammed Al-Hakim.
AIK attack but Karol Mets's header doesn't find the target.
Mjallby have a goal kick.
In the minute 88, Mjallby's Moses Ogbu misses with an attempt on goal.
Mohammed Al-Hakim awards AIK a goal kick.
Mjallby awarded a free kick in their own half.
Viktor Agardius is back on the pitch.
The fourth official's board shows 6 minutes, which will be added to the 2nd half.
Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of AIK.
Mohammed Al-Hakim signals a free kick to AIK.
Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
Mjallby needs to be cautious. AIK have an attacking throw-in.
Henok Goitom (AIK) is given an opening but the shot is blocked by a defender.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
The match has come to a close in Hallevik. The final score is 3-1.
The match at Strandvallen has been interrupted briefly for a check on Viktor Agardius, who is down injured.
